      <title>花旗集团在大规模重组期间削减了美国科技银行家的职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/citigroup-cut-us-tech-banker-jobs-amid-broad-reorganization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，花旗集团上周在其美国投资银行实施了新一轮裁员，这家金融巨头完成了计划中的重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/citigroup-cut-us-tech-banker-jobs-amid-broad-reorganization</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
